<br>
There is a lot of talk in this thread about &quot;spanking&quot; and &quot;teaching a child respect&quot; .  Well, respect is the last thing you are going to get if you resort to violence to get your point across.   <br>
<br>
I was never spanked as a child and I totally respected my parents.  Violence begets violence.  Disrespect begets disrespect.  If you disrespect your children by spanking them, don't be surprised when your children disrespect you.<br>
